name: LiveKitWebRTC-LK
summary: LiveKit WebRTC with LK-prefixed types for JMLiveKit
description:
Custom WebRTC build for LiveKit with LK-prefixed Objective-C symbols.
This is a modified version of the official LiveKitWebRTC that provides
LK-prefixed type aliases for compatibility with JMLiveKit.

Includes types like:
* LKRTCVideoRotation
* LKRTCSdpType  
* LKRTCIceConnectionState
* LKRTCDataChannel
* And all other LK-prefixed WebRTC types
